How to install a custom package

create a distributions folder and setup.py

cd to distributions folder and copy your package files ie Generaldistribution.py and Gaussiandistribution.py.
Also create a __init__.py file with text 'from .Gaussiandistribution import Gaussian'.

now cd back to the folder which contains the setup.py file and distributions folder and run the cmd
pip install .

verify with `pip freeze` that the package is installed